# GitHub Copilot Working Preferences

## Code Change Format
- For single function changes: Provide only the modified function
- For files with multiple changes throughout: Provide the entire file contents

## Version Control Approach
- Prefer direct changes over creating forks for minor fixes
- Document changes in commit messages with clear descriptions of what was modified

## Communication Style
- Provide concise explanations focused on technical details
- Include comments in code to explain complex logic

